snippet.textDisplay:
I wish some people would listen with an open mind. And stop comparing Strings with Rohail Hayat. 
They're both brilliant in their own way. Taking over from RH was no mean feat for Strings. 
Anyone that comes to this platform without a blank canvas, should go somewhere else to listen to music. 
Personally I think it's all bloody brilliant!! 
On the other hand, I like some of the 'worth reading' comments others are putting on here. 😊
